content:
GN128 Solutions an IT Solutions firm dedicated to helping clients leverage Information Technology to Increase profitability & efficiency.

We are recruiting to fill the position below:

Job Position: Junior Recruitment Officer

Job Location: Lagos

Summary


	We are a business based in Lagos currently looking to hire a Recruitment Officer to work in our office in Ikeja.
	You will be required to have excellent communications, administration and organizational skills.


Job Description





     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});






	Screening prospective job applicants to evaluate their skills and qualifications
	Entering job applicants’ CVs and contact details into the company database for future reference
	Revamping potential job candidates CVs to ensure that they are an excellent match for the client company
	Producing and posting job adverts that attract appropriate candidates
	Cold calling companies to promote recruitment services
	Meeting with new clients to develop and expand business opportunities
	Headhunting specific candidates for specific job roles
	Achieving recruitment quotas and business development targets each month.


Job Responsibilities


	Generate New Employer Leads & Maintain contact with exiting Employer clients;
	Use of online & social media platforms to source for prospective employees;
	Online & Site based screening of all applicants and Identifying suitable candidates;
	Ensure all applicants attending an interview are suitable for the roles;
	Co-ordinate the interview process with candidates and clients;
	Review and evaluate current recruitment process to ensure a smooth and efficient service;
	You will be required to perform any other required task as assigned to this role.


Person Specification


	Experienced in creating CV's + Cover Letters from existing CV;
	Experienced in making phone calls to a minimum of 20 contacts a day & documenting the calls;
	Use of online & social media platforms to generate Leads of prospective Employers;
	Respond to employee requests promptly and in a professional manner;
	Strong orientation to achieving team's goals and targets set;
	Ability to create daily report of operations;
	Very good level of English Language - both written and spoken;
	Excellent communication and interpersonal skills;
	Excellent Telephone handling skills;
	Excellent Computer Literacy & Record Keeping Skills;
	Excellent Administrative and Organizational skills
	Ability to work with own Initiative
	Strong orientation to achieving team's goals and targets set;
	Willingness to learn and develop;
	Team player open to share knowledge and to support your colleagues;
	Call Centre Experience will be an advantage;
	Professional attitude and orientation to details.


Salary
Basic From N150,000 + Bonus.

Method of Application
Interested and qualified candidates should send their CV to: recruit@gn128.com using "Recruitment Officer Position" as the subject of the msil.

Note: Only candidates that live in Lagos and within 30mins commuting of Ikeja would be considered.    



